    "content": "<p>The distribution of monthly expenditure of Ramesh on various items is shown in the following pie chart.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m06592h9/63596e6e-2e16-4037-b0df-0af317cf59aa/a55697d0-60fe-11ef-a495-011539d502ba/file-jaoe38c1m06592ha.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m06592h9/63596e6e-2e16-4037-b0df-0af317cf59aa/a55697d0-60fe-11ef-a495-011539d502ba/file-jaoe38c1m06592ha.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"SSC CGL Tier I - 27th July 2023 Shift 3 Quantitative Aptitude - Bar Chart &amp; Pie chart Question 8 English\"></p>\n\n<p>If the monthly income of Ramesh is ₹45,000, then find his total monthly expenditure (in ₹) on housing and transportation.</p>\n",
