    "comprehension": null,
    "content": "<p>The following bar chart shows the trends of foreign direct investment (FDI) into India from all over the world.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"SSC CGL Tier I - 26th July 2023 Shift 1 Quantitative Aptitude - Bar Chart &amp; Pie chart Question 1 English\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m0d4cqs1/d40aa4ca-ade7-4e44-bf55-7017351c34fb/9ef40010-64d4-11ef-a7c6-9be208601ae8/file-jaoe38c1m0d4cqs2.png?format=png\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m0d4cqs1/d40aa4ca-ade7-4e44-bf55-7017351c34fb/9ef40010-64d4-11ef-a7c6-9be208601ae8/file-jaoe38c1m0d4cqs2.png\"></p>\n\n<p>What was the average of India's FDI over the years 1992 - 1995 (rounded off to the nearest integer)?</p>\n",
    "options": [
